        -: 1898:// Implements the ResultOf() matcher for matching a return value of a
        -: 1899:// unary function of an object.
        -: 1900:template <typename Callable, typename InnerMatcher>
        -: 1901:class ResultOfMatcher {
        -: 1902: public:
